  "title": "Page Maker - Text Render Actor Animation & Layout Tool",
  "description": "Easily animate ANY text render actor in seconds!",
  "longDescription": "<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/DE-tqct3gMg\" rel=\"nofollow\">Page Maker Demo</a></p><p><br /></p><p>This tool is very simple to use! There are 4 animation types available, and a range of options on each of these animation types. You can easily combine animations, and apply these to ANY text render actor. You can also just use one of my BP_Page actors to do this all EVEN EASIER.</p><p><br /></p><p>Aside from animation, this tool empowers you to easily wrap your text, constraining either the width or the height of your text block! Very helpful for procedurally generated text actors.</p>",
